from elw subject re lds gordon question on the nicene creed the nicene creed we believe in one god the of of thing visible invisible in one lord jesus christ the only-begotten son of god beget of the before world god of god light of light very god of very god beget not be of one with the by whom thing be who for u men for our down from by the holy spirit of the virgin crucify for u under pontius he suffer bury the third rise to the scriptur e into sitteth on the right of the he come with glory to judge both the quick the whose kingdom no end we believe in the holy spirit the lord giver of life who proceedeth from the the son who with the the son together be worship glorify who speak by the prophet we believe in one holy church we one for the remission of sin we look for the resurrection of the the life of the world to come 